Experiencing creator burnout. Bear with me here 🙌
 I have been working so hard creating new stuff. 
It’s very difficult to try and be present, network but also be the creator at the same time. 😅
I decided what’s most important is to keep on creating no matter what even if that means being MIA for a few days and allow myself to immerse in my art rather than post a bunch of selfies or things that are random to try and stay a float ….
Quality not quantity 🫶 
By the way, do you think those roses are real? 👀
